content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4206.3 - Public telephones

State Regulations

All public telephones on the track grounds shall be
locked 15 minutes prior to the sale of pari-mutuel tickets and remain closed
until 15 minutes after the last race has been certified
official. Notes
